This is my custom ~/.vim folder
google-chrome --headless  --disable-gpu  --screenshot  -window-size=1280,3000 https://github.com/grandyang/leetcode/issues/812



required debian packages:
    + vim (of course...)
    + gvim (for vim-server)
    + ctags ( <F8> and <F9> shortcut)
    + libxml2 {xmllint} (<F2> shortcut)
